  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><p>It is very important to practice writing hiragana every day, which will enable you to master what you have learned faster. If you have any questions, you can always ask other students and teachers in the group <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/communities/Q29tbXVuaXR5LTM1MzQ=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p><p>Please download the first hiragana practice here <a class=\"fr-file\" href=\"../../pdfs/week_01/day_01/Hiragana_Practice_Day_1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Hiragana Practice Day 1.pdf</a> and watch the 2 videos below to see the stroke order:</p><p><strong>あ、い、う、え、お</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/buh5sv3i57dcbr63ol6g\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"Hiragana 1 あいうえお.mp4 - 01:34\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span></strong></p><p><strong>か、き、く、け、こ</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/buh5t3mje35bt9cic340\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"Hiragana 2 かきくけこ.mp4 - 01:32\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span></strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: initial;\">If you want more tools to help you learn and practice stroke order and pronunciation, you can use the free trial course provided by the Go! Go! Nihon&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"background-color: initial;\">Hiragana Quest app</strong><span style=\"background-color: initial;\">&nbsp;(you can purchase all Hiragana courses for &yen;360), please click&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://futuretrostudios.com/hiraganaquest/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here</a><span style=\"background-color: initial;\">.</span></p></div>",
